91
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:13,970
Fine. I'm going to pick up my girlfriend.

92
00:07:14,850 --> 00:07:18,390
Get lost. As if you're the only one with a girlfriend.

93
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:21,120
You got that right.

94
