Miaomiao, why are you treating us differently?

102
00:08:37,670 --> 00:08:39,460
I didn't.

103
00:08:39,460 --> 00:08:44,130
When we showed up earlier, I didn't see you come running out to welcome us.

104
00:08:44,850 --> 00:08:47,570
Ignore her. She's just envious.

105
00:08:47,570 --> 00:08:49,250
