Xinxin.

111
00:09:03,780 --> 00:09:04,760
Don't bother explaining.

112
00:09:04,760 --> 00:09:08,330
I now have a huge issue with your boyfriend.

113
00:09:12,090 --> 00:09:14,270
Let's go.

114
00:09:14,270 --> 00:09:18,630
Xia, let's not be the third wheel.

115
00:09:32,540 --> 00:09:34,310
Here.

116
00:09:40,660 --> 00:09:43,600
Keep drawing. I'll keep you company.

117
