Senior, between these two, which one do you think is nicer?

118
00:09:56,860 --> 00:09:59,270
Pardon? Aren't they the same?

119
00:09:59,270 --> 00:10:04,060
They aren't. One has buttons and the other doesn't.

120
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:05,690
I see.

121
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:09,000
So which one is better?

122
00:10:14,030 --> 00:10:16,210
Without buttons?

123
00:10:16,210 --> 00:10:18,170
Really?

124
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:25,820
But with buttons as embellishments, I think it will create a unique visual focus.

125
00:10:25,820 --> 00:10:27,610
- Is that so?
- Yeah.

126
00:10:28,270 --> 00:10:30,900
So the one with buttons then?

127
00:10:32,310 --> 00:10:38,920
But I'm worried that with buttons, it will draw people's attention away from the cut of the skirt.

128
00:10:39,540 --> 00:10:41,750
Then without buttons.

129
