249
00:20:35,310 --> 00:20:39,180
Even though our electric car is a little slow, but he should have arrived by daybreak.

250
00:20:39,180 --> 00:20:41,080
It's already been over a week.

251
00:20:41,080 --> 00:20:44,140
The security deposit he left isn't enough.

252
00:20:44,140 --> 00:20:45,570
He was supposed to return it a few days ago.

253
00:20:45,570 --> 00:20:47,450
But he hasn't brought it back. Now, his phone isn't even ringing.

254
00:20:47,450 --> 00:20:50,680
Buddy, don't say anymore.

255
00:20:51,400 --> 00:20:54,340
Right now, I feel a lot like crying.

256
00:20:58,430 --> 00:20:59,790
Lin Kaituo

257
00:21:05,950 --> 00:21:09,700
Sorry, no one is answering the number you dialed. Please dial again later.

258
00:21:09,700 --> 00:21:13,550
I'm done for. Lin Kaituo must be mad.

259
00:21:15,110 --> 00:21:17,950
- Hey!
- Kaituo, let's play some basketball.

260
00:21:25,930 --> 00:21:28,350
What's wrong? Did you eat some dynamite?

261
00:21:28,350 --> 00:21:30,390
What are you doing in our dorm?

262
00:21:31,910 --> 00:21:34,060
I've been calling you all day and it's not ringing.

263
00:21:34,060 --> 00:21:37,070
He Xin left today. Why didn't you come to see her off?

264
00:21:39,110 --> 00:21:41,630
It broke yesterday.

265
00:21:52,790 --> 00:21:54,640
Who provoked our buddy, Kaituo?

266
00:21:54,640 --> 00:21:58,350
If your phone is broken, just get it repaired.

267
00:21:58,350 --> 00:22:00,750
I've been a little unlucky recently.

268
00:22:01,460 --> 00:22:04,230
What bad luck? Tell me about it.

269
00:22:04,230 --> 00:22:06,460
Get out.

270
00:22:06,460 --> 00:22:09,770
How can I give you advice if you don't tell me about it?

271
00:22:18,780 --> 00:22:22,820
She actually refused me. Tell me, does she have a heart?

272
00:22:25,460 --> 00:22:29,910
So you're saying, you picked up and brought that express package to He Xin from so far away.

273
00:22:29,940 --> 00:22:33,980
Then, you even borrowed a pedicab from someone; then on the way back to return it, it broke down.

274
00:22:33,980 --> 00:22:38,050
They've been trying to repair it for over a week and aren't done yet.

275
00:22:38,050 --> 00:22:41,480
Then, you carefully prepared a gift for He Xin and while you were in the process of preparing it, you dropped your phone and broke it.

276
00:22:41,480 --> 00:22:44,790
Finally, you confessed to He Xin and she didn't think you were sincere.

277
00:22:46,040 --> 00:22:48,870
Did you have to repeat all that?

278
00:22:51,130 --> 00:22:56,390
Our buddy, Kaituo, really... it's enough to bring me to tears.

279
00:22:59,850 --> 00:23:03,190
So what's your advice?

280
00:23:06,560 --> 00:23:09,190
You have really suffered.

281
00:23:09,190 --> 00:23:11,230
My advice is...

282
00:23:12,240 --> 00:23:14,630
run into a wall.

283
00:23:26,870 --> 00:23:29,710
Not calling anymore. Do as you wish!

284
00:23:38,870 --> 00:23:41,480
Then I sincerely reject you.

285
00:23:48,220 --> 00:23:51,790
Then I sincerely reject you?

286
00:23:52,510 --> 00:23:56,880
He Xin, He Xin, why were you pretending to be cool?

287
00:23:59,620 --> 00:24:04,070
How do you still have the face to call him now?

288
00:24:16,950 --> 00:24:19,430
Is there really no one in the model classroom?

289
00:24:19,430 --> 00:24:23,910
I'm worried that the seats in the fashion major classrooms are all taken.

290
00:24:23,960 --> 00:24:28,020
There's really no one. Ten minutes won't make a difference so eat slowly, don't choke.

291
00:24:28,020 --> 00:24:32,170
I can't. My schedule is really packed.

292
00:24:33,110 --> 00:24:37,670
I said that take-out was fine but you insisted on making me come to the cafeteria.

293
00:24:39,880 --> 00:24:41,490
Let's go.

294
00:24:44,050 --> 00:24:46,670
I'm full.

295
00:24:48,880 --> 00:24:51,150
I'll bring it back to the classroom to drink.

296
00:24:52,940 --> 00:24:55,430
Sit down and finish it.

297
00:25:01,790 --> 00:25:04,720
I have to make clothes and practice basketball.

298
00:25:04,720 --> 00:25:07,050
And you're even making me sit down and finish this.

299
00:25:07,050 --> 00:25:08,980
What are you saying?

300
00:25:09,480 --> 00:25:11,280
Nothing.

301
00:25:25,580 --> 00:25:28,670
I'm finished, can we go now?

302
00:25:31,840 --> 00:25:35,270
- Okay, let's go, let's go.
- You take the tray.

303
00:26:54,170 --> 00:26:57,350
When I was younger, this was how my mom helped me stop the bleeding.

304
00:27:00,330 --> 00:27:04,380
- Right now...
- What is it?

305
00:27:04,390 --> 00:27:06,860
You really look like a vampire.

306
00:27:07,730 --> 00:27:11,070
- Hurry and finish this, so we can go back.
- Yes.

307
00:27:27,990 --> 00:27:30,280
Senior, look!

308
00:28:22,370 --> 00:28:25,830
Haicheng University

309
00:28:26,750 --> 00:28:29,260
It's almost the end of the term. When are you coming back?

310
00:28:29,260 --> 00:28:31,750
You call me once a day urging me.

311
00:28:31,800 --> 00:28:34,150
Those who don't know us probably think you're my boyfriend.

312
00:28:34,150 --> 00:28:36,270
I'm about to die from loneliness.

313
00:28:36,270 --> 00:28:41,550
After Miaomiao submitted all her applications, she's been stuck in the library studying for her IELTS.

314
00:28:41,590 --> 00:28:44,640
I'm the only person in this dorm all day.

315
00:28:44,640 --> 00:28:47,630
I'm so lonely that I'm even starting to miss Tang Mengfei.

316
00:28:48,440 --> 00:28:50,380
Where did Tang Mengfei go off to?

317
00:28:50,380 --> 00:28:53,280
I think she's signed on with a modeling company.

318
00:28:53,280 --> 00:28:54,950
She's rarely here.

319
00:28:54,950 --> 00:28:56,080
That's good then.

320
00:28:56,080 --> 00:28:57,660
He Xin!

321
00:28:57,660 --> 00:28:58,940
Coming!

322
00:28:58,940 --> 00:29:02,390
- I've got to go. Bye-bye.
 - What?!

323
00:29:15,260 --> 00:29:17,900
Do you want to eat one?

324
00:29:21,880 --> 00:29:24,570
- Senior Sister!
- What's wrong?

325
00:29:24,570 --> 00:29:25,750
You're back?

326
00:29:25,750 --> 00:29:27,840
I'm so lonely, keep me company.

327
00:29:27,840 --> 00:29:29,540
Let's go eat.

328
00:29:30,340 --> 00:29:32,960
But I have to go back to my dad's company later.

329
00:29:32,960 --> 00:29:36,630
He has a project recently that I need to learn from.

330
00:29:40,250 --> 00:29:42,470
It's okay.

331
00:29:43,620 --> 00:29:46,860
Why is everyone so busy?

332
00:29:57,040 --> 00:29:59,350
- Hey, A Xia.
- Yes?

333
00:30:00,080 --> 00:30:02,730
That...

334
00:30:02,730 --> 00:30:05,270
Does this taste good?

335
00:30:05,270 --> 00:30:08,930
- It's okay. If you want it, you can have it.
- All right.

336
00:30:13,020 --> 00:30:16,060
It must be pretty busy for those in your major lately.

337
00:30:16,060 --> 00:30:17,630
It's not busy.

338
00:30:17,630 --> 00:30:20,830
Then it must be pretty busy for those in year three.

339
00:30:20,830 --> 00:30:24,460
That's true. They're getting ready for internships.

340
00:30:27,000 --> 00:30:32,830
That Senior Da Chao of yours hasn't been showing up lately, has he?

341
00:30:33,520 --> 00:30:36,000
Senior Da Chao?

342
00:30:36,900 --> 00:30:41,160
I heard he recently entered a famous fashion company as an intern.

343
00:30:41,160 --> 00:30:43,800
He comes back totally exhausted every day.

344
00:30:43,800 --> 00:30:45,160
- Oh, Senior Sister!
- Yes?

345
00:30:45,160 --> 00:30:49,390
If you're looking for him for anything, I can help connect you guys.

346
00:30:49,390 --> 00:30:52,180
No, no. I'm not looking for him, I'll head off first.

347
00:30:53,000 --> 00:30:55,420
Bye-bye!

348
00:31:16,750 --> 00:31:18,590
What are you doing here?

349
00:31:18,590 --> 00:31:21,150
Where are you going? I'll go with you.

350
00:31:21,150 --> 00:31:23,550
- You're just getting back?
- Right.

351
00:31:23,550 --> 00:31:26,140
I just got off work, it was an all nighter.

352
00:31:26,140 --> 00:31:28,150
Then you better go back and get some rest.

353
00:31:28,190 --> 00:31:30,110
It's okay, I'm wide awake.

354
00:31:30,110 --> 00:31:32,070
Where are you going? I'll go with you.

355
00:31:32,070 --> 00:31:35,790
It's really okay. It's not really convenient where I'm going.

356
00:31:37,440 --> 00:31:41,230
That's true. You didn't like me tagging along to begin with anyway.

357
00:31:41,820 --> 00:31:43,570
Th-That's not what I meant.

358
00:31:43,570 --> 00:31:47,980
It's okay. Then I'll go back and catch up on sleep. Take care on the road.

359
00:31:47,980 --> 00:31:50,140
Bye-bye.

360
00:32:18,030 --> 00:32:20,530
Senior Sister Miaomiao.

361
00:32:20,530 --> 00:32:22,220
Hello.

362
00:32:25,410 --> 00:32:28,470
Wow, you have such a great mindset.

363
00:32:28,470 --> 00:32:32,980
The results for the exchange students come out today, yet you're still studying here so calmly.

364
00:32:32,980 --> 00:32:35,600
You truly are so great.

365
00:32:36,260 --> 00:32:38,240
Today?

366
00:32:38,240 --> 00:32:39,880
Yeah.

367
00:32:41,300 --> 00:32:43,940
I forgot! I thought it was tomorrow.

368
00:32:43,940 --> 00:32:47,890
Don't be anxious, Senior. I already helped you check it.

369
00:32:47,890 --> 00:32:49,640
Thanks.

370
00:32:52,470 --> 00:32:57,510
Take a look. This is the initial design draft submitted by the overseas architect.

371
00:32:57,510 --> 00:33:01,980
Honestly, compared to our initial draft,

372
00:33:01,980 --> 00:33:05,300
his draft is more practical.

373
00:33:05,300 --> 00:33:08,030
Teacher, didn't we already get the project?

374
00:33:08,030 --> 00:33:11,360
How come there's still an overseas architect participating?

375
00:33:11,360 --> 00:33:13,950
This is how the Fang Corporation has operated all along.

376
00:33:13,950 --> 00:33:17,380
They have domestic architects and international architects collaborate

377
00:33:17,380 --> 00:33:19,820
to create the best design.

378
00:33:20,630 --> 00:33:25,670
Then if that's the case, will disagreements over design ideas cause us to be unable to work together?

379
00:33:25,670 --> 00:33:30,110
After you guys enter the industry, you'll find that these sorts of collaborations are very common.

380
00:33:30,110 --> 00:33:32,930
It especially tests your communication skills.

381
00:33:33,860 --> 00:33:37,230
I think my communication skills are fine.

382
00:33:38,100 --> 00:33:41,570
Is this Frank the last Pritzker Architecture winner?

383
00:33:41,570 --> 00:33:42,750
That's right.

384
00:33:42,750 --> 00:33:44,850
Wow, he's that amazing?

385
00:33:44,860 --> 00:33:47,670
Then isn't it to our benefit that we get to be on the same project as him?

386
00:33:47,670 --> 00:33:52,420
That's why having you guys join the project will broaden your horizons.

387
00:33:52,420 --> 00:33:55,700
It's just too bad that Liang Younian can't stay around for the entire project.

388
00:33:55,700 --> 00:33:57,880
Teacher, you can't abandon me.

389
00:33:57,880 --> 00:34:02,210
Even if I'm abroad, I still have internet. I can share my progress with you at any time.

390
00:34:03,070 --> 00:34:07,320
Okay. Take back the design draft and think about it.

391
00:34:07,320 --> 00:34:10,940
Then we'll analyze it in detail and next time, we'll head to Fang Corporation for a meeting.

392
00:34:10,940 --> 00:34:12,510
Okay.

393
00:34:28,140 --> 00:34:30,010
It's Miaomiao. Go without me.

394
00:34:30,010 --> 00:34:32,650
You prioritize your girlfriend over your friend.

395
00:34:34,450 --> 00:34:36,140
Hello?

396
00:34:37,020 --> 00:34:41,150
Senior. I got into the exchange program.

397
00:34:41,980 --> 00:34:46,120
Really? Where are you now? I'll go to you.

398
00:34:46,120 --> 00:34:49,070
I'm at the entrance of the library.

399
00:35:54,900 --> 00:35:56,700
Xia Miaomiao.

400
00:35:56,700 --> 00:35:58,330
What is my name?

401
00:35:59,320 --> 00:36:00,760
I don't.

402
00:36:00,760 --> 00:36:02,550
You don't have a brain?

403
00:36:12,670 --> 00:36:15,310
I'll pack up right now.

404
00:36:18,990 --> 00:36:22,760
- Hello, Senior.
- Hello.

405
00:36:24,580 --> 00:36:27,710
I can start applying for my passport.

406
00:36:27,710 --> 00:36:30,790
Miaomiao, when will you apply for your passport? Recently, I also—

407
00:36:30,790 --> 00:36:32,590
You'll also be doing what?

408
00:36:34,590 --> 00:36:36,910
Nothing.

409
00:36:39,550 --> 00:36:41,380
Let's go.

410
00:37:12,340 --> 00:37:16,910
Senior, we don't need to be in such a rush to get a head shot.

411
00:37:17,660 --> 00:37:20,790
We need to get our pictures taken today in order to apply for passports tomorrow.

412
00:37:20,790 --> 00:37:25,340
It's already Friday. What then? Should we wait until Monday?

413
00:37:25,340 --> 00:37:27,490
We'll still be in time on Monday.

414
00:37:27,490 --> 00:37:30,910
Besides, I haven't taken the IELTS yet.

415
00:37:35,530 --> 00:37:37,940
We'll apply for our passports whenever you say.

416
00:37:37,940 --> 00:37:40,520
There isn't any class tomorrow anyway.

417
00:37:46,990 --> 00:37:50,280
Senior, what's wrong?

418
00:37:52,060 --> 00:37:54,160
Nothing.

419
00:38:04,210 --> 00:38:07,790
Why does Wang Yutian still keep...

420
00:38:59,820 --> 00:39:01,610
Look!

421
00:39:01,610 --> 00:39:04,340
You're on the display window, Senior.

422
00:39:08,820 --> 00:39:10,990
You look great.

423
00:39:10,990 --> 00:39:13,640
Excuse me. Do you want to get your photo taken?

424
00:39:13,640 --> 00:39:14,990
Yes.

425
00:39:14,990 --> 00:39:19,030
Yes, she needs to have a passport photo for her visa.

426
00:39:19,070 --> 00:39:21,110
Sure, we can do that. Chang, get this done.

427
00:39:21,110 --> 00:39:22,710
All right, come with me. This way.

428
00:39:22,710 --> 00:39:24,420
Wait for me.

429
00:39:28,390 --> 00:39:34,370
By the way, Sir. Why is my photo in your display window?

430
00:39:34,370 --> 00:39:39,580
This photo was taken very well. I only put it up after I asked your dad for his consent last time.

431
00:39:40,820 --> 00:39:43,940
But I personally didn't know about this.

432
00:39:43,980 --> 00:39:47,540
Please take it down. This is a bit awkward.

433
00:39:47,580 --> 00:39:51,230
I see. Sure, I'll get them to take it down later.

434
00:39:51,270 --> 00:39:52,580
Have a seat first.

435
00:39:52,580 --> 00:39:54,140
- Thank you.
- Head shots are fast.

436
00:39:54,180 --> 00:39:56,150
- Thank you, Sir.
- Sure.

437
00:40:09,750 --> 00:40:12,110
Pick up your photos tomorrow with this slip.

438
00:40:12,150 --> 00:40:13,790
Sure, thank you.

439
00:40:14,910 --> 00:40:19,920
Young man, your girlfriend just said that when her head shot is ready, she wants it displayed with yours.

440
00:40:19,920 --> 00:40:22,590
- But you just said—
- Sir!

441
00:40:24,000 --> 00:40:26,230
Just leave it up then.

442
00:40:28,460 --> 00:40:30,870
- Let's go.
- Sure.

443
00:40:31,730 --> 00:40:33,940
- Thank you.
- Take care.

444
00:40:35,700 --> 00:40:38,190
It's great to be young.

445
00:40:57,590 --> 00:41:01,590
Student, why do you keep looking at me?

446
00:41:01,590 --> 00:41:03,460
I didn't.

447
00:41:04,500 --> 00:41:08,790
I just... I just really want to thank you.

448
00:41:09,740 --> 00:41:11,700
What for?

449
00:41:12,980 --> 00:41:18,510
Thank you. You've made me into a better person.

450
00:41:19,110 --> 00:41:22,670
Thank you for treating me to this drink.

451
00:41:22,710 --> 00:41:25,370
Just for that?

452
00:41:25,370 --> 00:41:27,870
How do you plan on thanking me?

453
00:41:28,950 --> 00:41:31,230
I'll buy you some as well.

454
00:41:32,200 --> 00:41:34,790
How many?

455
00:41:35,860 --> 00:41:39,740
Ten cups.

456
00:41:43,120 --> 00:41:45,420
Then you'll have to make it ten times more.

457
00:41:46,430 --> 00:41:50,720
I can't afford that many. How about something else?

458
00:41:51,590 --> 00:41:53,790
Something else?

459
00:42:57,090 --> 00:42:59,100
What are you two doing?

460
00:43:04,060 --> 00:43:09,700
My neck doesn't feel great these days.

461
00:43:12,030 --> 00:43:14,910
- What are you doing?
- Walking the dog.

462
00:43:14,910 --> 00:43:16,970
Are you done?

463
00:43:16,970 --> 00:43:18,820
Let's go home.

464
00:43:18,900 --> 00:43:20,930
Sure.

